@JimBobCooter00 Dear Sirs,
we are very sorry for your negative experience.
We kindly inform you that you can contact our customer relation on the following link for flights irregularities: Post-flight assistance | Air Dolomiti

@JMccalljm @British_Airways @HeathrowAirport @MUC_Airport @FlyMilanLinate Dear Jamir,
we kindly invite you to fill in this form, where you can write a report about what happened to your Air Dolomiti flight: https://t.co/54prB2goa1 
Our colleagues will take care of your request. Thank you very much, your feedback is important to us.
